items.title: LA turns to Kershaw to end 11-game slide
items.summary: Two pitchers making their third starts since injuries will battle Tuesday at AT&T Park. The Dodgers, trying to snap a Los Angeles-record 11-game losing streak, will send lefty Clayton Kershaw to the bump while the Giants will hand the ball to Johnny Cueto .
